data.description: Great open floor plan with 4 bed 2.5 bath and master down. The kitchen has plenty of cabinet and counter space with a pantry and is open to the living room. Primary bedroom has a huge walk in closet and a large full bath. Upstairs has 3 bedrooms and a loft/office area. The garage has custom built in storage for any project and the attic has built in storage area. The community has a pool and two playgrounds. This is a must see for any family!
